name: Rain Doll
description: Three rainy days in a row. On one of those days, a sugar glider stopped by in my dream. He just stared and settled on the roof of the house. At first glance I asked, did he cause this local rain? I hastily threw my clothes on the roof and made a strange movement, like a rain charmer. I like rain, cause at that time my heart feels like cool and warm at the same time. However, that day I just wanted to go out without the rain and buy some noodles.
